             ANGULAR

Basic Building Blocks

1.module-to import 3rd party modules(root module-app.module.ts)
2.component -to create html,css and ts files


Basic commands

1.to create  new project-ng new projectname
2.to create new component-ng g componentname
3.to run angular files-ng serve --open

basic concept

data binding-share data between components
ts=component 
html=view
1) one way data binding
data sharing only one direction
   1.1)component to view and to view to component(ts-html or html to ts)
        a)string interpolation- {(expression)}
        b)property binding -[attribute_name]="property"

        1.2)view to component(html to cs)
        a)event binding-(event name)="function_name()"
        b)event binding using $event-(event_name)="function_name($event)"
        c)event binding using template referencing variable- #variable_name

        2) two way data binding

        data sharing in both direction(ts->html html->cs)
        i)ng model binding-import formsmodule in app.module.ts
        [(ngmodel)]="property name"

